com.facebook.litho.annotations

Annotation Type OnCalculateCachedValue


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface OnCalculateCachedValue
    Annotation for a method on a component's spec that indicates that the method is used to calculate a value that is cached by the component, and may be access in methods using CachedValue.

    • Required Element Summary

      Required Elements 
      Modifier and Type Required Element and Description
      String name 

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract String name
        Returns:
        the name of the CachedValue that is being calculated.
